{"tid":759383,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［新樓平過二手樓］【將軍澳新盤】晉海2期售出15伙","createTime":"2018-07-28T14:28:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-30T09:04:51.000Z","uid":122377,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c700bdb32f52542a1de5e42f8b77f36c03ffa1d7","tid":759383,"uid":122377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T14:28:40.000Z","msg":"新地（016）近期積極推盤，其中將軍澳日出康城新盤晉海2期今日開售21伙貨尾，即日售出15伙，套現約1.2億元。<br />\n<br />\n一手成交紀錄冊顯示，晉海2期今日售出15伙，單位分佈3A、5A及5B座，實用面積由343方呎至626方呎，成交價介乎634.68萬元至1,096.65萬元，<span style=\"color: red;\">呎價15,045元至19,448元</span>。其中最貴一伙為5B座9樓B室，實用面積626方呎，以1,096.65萬元成交，呎價17,518元。合共套現約1.2億元。<br />\n<br />\n又賣唔哂 尺價又平 <br />\n發展商又做善事？"},{"pid":"56f0ca358358884f1fefb299392e6d3527ee6d49","tid":759383,"uid":132461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T08:22:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"286824ad46025f68870562b980f350fdb0fff7eb","tid":759383,"uid":4052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T08:25:27.000Z","msg":"搞手但求打個和啫"},{"pid":"548b29aad6d04fe9c697a126fb102a907508e232","tid":759383,"uid":193436,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T08:27:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9a2380ed1a551bec75b93a8dda0fa72956e36c38","tid":759383,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T08:27:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"db66356777895b58c8c90fc9a357a7d770865fde","tid":759383,"uid":81698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T08:29:16.000Z","msg":"呎價萬5蚊將軍澳真係幾平 特價時段 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79cfb685a60e65422f537eb5158798c48cc25c99","tid":759383,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r